<slide title="Horde">
<link href="http://www.horde.org/" align="center">http://www.horde.org/</link>
<list>
 <bullet>An application framework with a number of groupware-related applications</bullet>
 <bullet>Built on top of PEAR, including PEAR::DB for database abstraction</bullet>
 <bullet>IMP: Webmail</bullet>
 <bullet>Jonah: Portal</bullet>
 <bullet>Kronolith: Calendar</bullet>
 <bullet>WHUPS: Problem Tracking</bullet>
 <bullet>Turba: Address book, contact management</bullet>
 <bullet>Chora: CVS viewer</bullet>
 <bullet>Mnemo: Note manager</bullet>
 <bullet>Nag: Task manager</bullet>
 <bullet>Sork: Account management</bullet>
 <bullet>Orator: Presentation software</bullet>
</list>

